    "body": "Hey, @shehinfn, I looked into the code and found that these CLI options are dependent on each other\r\n```\r\n@Value.Derived\r\n  default int getTxPoolMaxFutureTransactionByAccount() {\r\n    return (int) Math.ceil(getTxPoolLimitByAccountPercentage() * getTxPoolMaxSize());\r\n  }\r\n```\r\n[tx-pool-max-size](https://besu.hyperledger.org/stable/public-networks/reference/cli/options#tx-pool-max-size)\r\n[tx-pool-limit-account-percentage](https://besu.hyperledger.org/stable/public-networks/reference/cli/options#tx-pool-limit-by-account-percentage)\r\nTry looking into these two options, I was able to get around 1000 TPS after using these.",
